title: Face Off: Can Demi Vollering and FDJ-Suez Sink SD Worx?
content:
Vollering's acrimonious split from SD Worx was the sensation of last season. Our editors debate whether she can live up to the hype and lift FDJ to super team status.

Read the full article at Face Off: Can Demi Vollering and FDJ-Suez Sink SD Worx? on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
